Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.78,0:27:51.98,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}本字幕由  動漫國&KNA&輕之國度字幕組  聯合製作\N僅供試看,請支持購買正版音像製品
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.99,0:27:56.78,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}翻譯:謎之人物H&えんさん&傻瓜三世   校對&時軸:傻瓜三世   後期:小聖
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:37.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}This is a fate that brought us here watch my long shot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Feel like I am falling into the flame of lies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:50.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Tell me what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Trying not to step back to where I used to belong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:57.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Looking for the escape from pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:01.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}I will cross my fingers hoping not to be sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:05.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}約束したんだ君とその希望に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:08.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Get in the raid Get ready for the time to come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:12.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}浮かび上がるシルエット追いかけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:15.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Drop down the reason why I'm standing here alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}May be it's already too late to regain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:24.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}運命としてかかげた灯を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:26.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:29.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}What if I could right my wrongs and save you from the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:39.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0\fs82.5}It's not enough It's not enough for me to break the rule upon this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:44.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}I will never gonna leave you never wanna lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:46.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}we'll make it in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:52.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Not backing down for real I won't trace someone else's life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}I know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:37.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}命運帶我們走到了這裡 見識我的豪賭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}彷彿落入了謊言的烈火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:50.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}請告訴我 你想讓我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}為了保護我所在的家園
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:57.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我尋找著逃脫苦難的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:01.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我握拳祈禱不會有人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:05.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我保證過不會放棄你和希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:08.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}做好準備 面對必將到來的侵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:12.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}追趕著腦海裡浮現的倩影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:15.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}捨棄掉孤獨戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}想奪回一切也許為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:24.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}但也不要遺失命運給你的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:26.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}再也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:29.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}如果我能改掉錯誤 救你於水火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:39.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}那也不夠我去打破這個世界的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:44.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我不會再丟下你 不會再失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:46.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我們一定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:52.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我決不後退 決不成為別人理想的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我知道我該過怎樣的人生
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.22,0:28:19.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}壊れないように優しく抱いて　溶けて涙流す
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.60,0:28:25.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そんな氷の人形みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.46,0:28:30.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}なれないから
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.68,0:28:42.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もう逃げない　知りたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:46.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}強く　I believe…believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.26,0:28:50.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}きっと一番の約束の言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.17,0:28:54.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}痛いくらい握って離さない
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.95,0:29:00.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}わがままな今連れて　誰のものでもない未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.70,0:29:03.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこから始めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.43,0:29:13.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}空を掴む(夢の欠片)　祈りの手を(指先まで)
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.73,0:29:18.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}伸ばすかぎり(生けるかぎり)
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.95,0:29:26.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこに本当はあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.22,0:28:19.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我當不了一隻冰做的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.60,0:28:25.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}將你小心翼翼地抱在懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.46,0:28:30.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}眼眶裡融化出晶瑩的淚珠
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.68,0:28:42.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}所以我不會再逃避  我想去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:46.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我會堅定地…堅定地相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.26,0:28:50.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}當初最放在心底裡的承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.17,0:28:54.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我會緊緊把握  絕不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.95,0:29:00.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}帶著任性的現在  從此邁步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.70,0:29:03.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}向著沒有人能把控的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.43,0:29:13.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}抓住空中(夢的碎片)  握掌祈求(併攏指尖)
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.73,0:29:18.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}用力伸出手臂(直到生命的盡頭)
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.95,0:29:26.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我終將發現真相
